9T07:43:25Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"OWNER","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"- 什么是` Ajax`? 如何创建一个`Ajax`？\r\n\r\n* `AJAX(Asynchronous Javascript And XML) `= 异步 `JavaScript` + `XML` 在后台与服务器进行异步数据交换，不用重载整个网页，实现局部刷新。\r\n\r\n* 创建 `ajax` 步骤：\r\n  - 1.创建 `XMLHttpRequest` 对象\r\n  - 2.创建一个新的 `HTTP` 请求，并指定该 `HTTP` 请求的类型、验证信息\r\n  - 3.设置响应 `HTTP` 请求状态变化的回调函数\r\n  - 4.发送 `HTTP` 请求\r\n  - 5.获取异步调用返回的数据\r\n  - 6.使用 `JavaScript` 和 `DOM` 实现局部刷新\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();\r\nxhr.open(\"POST\", url, true);\r\nxhr.setRequestHeader(\"Content-type\", \"application/x-www-form-urlencoded\");\r\nxhr.onreadystatechange = function () {\r\n    if (xhr.readyState == 4 && (xhr.status == 200 || xhr.status == 304)) {\r\n        fn.call(this, xhr.responseText);\r\n    }\r\n};\r\nxhr.send(data);\r\n```","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/hankliu62.github.com/issues/314/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/hankliu62.github.com/issues/314/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"menus":[]},"__N_SSG":true}